and see that the world
doesn't revolve around money.

87
00:04:09,498 --> 00:04:11,501
What?

88
00:04:11,667 --> 00:04:14,997
Nothing. Just... going to bat
for public schools,

89
00:04:15,122 --> 00:04:16,798
it's so not like you.

90
00:04:16,964 --> 00:04:20,837
You know, I would love
to help you with your auction.

91
00:04:20,962 --> 00:04:23,471
It'll give us a chance
to spend some time together.

92
00:04:23,637 --> 00:04:26,057
Really?

93
00:04:26,223 --> 00:04:28,310
Yeah.

94
