and they shouldn't be.

104
00:04:52,666 --> 00:04:55,170
Well, what have they told you?

105
00:04:55,336 --> 00:04:57,006
They told me Charlie Young,
or John Delario,

106
00:04:57,131 --> 00:04:58,958
or whatever the hell
he's calling himself,

107
00:04:59,083 --> 00:05:01,093
uh, that he shot and killed my wife

108
00:05:01,218 --> 00:05:02,552
and then he shot himself.

109
00:05:02,718 --> 00:05:05,055
But that's not everything.
There's more evidence.

110
00:05:05,221 --> 00:05:06,098
They found Bridget's fingerprints,

111
00:05:06,223 --> 00:05:08,651
the gun that was used to kill Gemma

112
00:05:08,776 --> 00:05:10,052
was traced back to Bridget.

113
00:05:10,177 --> 00:05:12,479
So why aren't they looking for her?

114
00:05:12,645 --> 00:05:15,358
Believe me, Mr. Butler,
I-I share your frustrations.

115
00:05:15,483 --> 00:05:16,508
It's a complicated situation...

116
00:05:16,633 --> 00:05:18,561
I can't get into the details...

117
00:05:18,686 --> 00:05:21,280
But trust me when I tell you
I haven't given up.

118
00:05:21,405 --> 00:05:23,573
I'm doing everything
I can to find Bridget.

119
00:05:23,739 --> 00:05:26,792
It doesn't make any sense.

120
00:05:28,912 --> 00:05:30,139
Gemma didn't know Bridget.

121
00:05:30,264 --> 00:05:33,249
