155
00:07:02,406 --> 00:07:04,550
we can always trade it in.

156
00:07:04,675 --> 00:07:06,652
Something smaller, perhaps?

157
00:07:06,777 --> 00:07:09,472
The only thing that I want
smaller is the band.

158
00:07:09,597 --> 00:07:11,957
(Chuckles)
It keeps falling off.

159
00:07:12,082 --> 00:07:14,477
I should probably
take it to get resized.

160
00:07:14,602 --> 00:07:17,563
Then the fit will be
as perfect as the rest of it.

161
00:07:17,688 --> 00:07:19,221
Mm!

162
00:07:32,118 --> 00:07:33,412
Thank you so much.

163
00:07:33,537 --> 00:07:35,081
I wanted to surprise my husband,

164
00:07:35,206 --> 00:07:36,615
but I forgot my keys.

165
00:07:36,740 --> 00:07:38,284
No problem.

166
00:07:38,409 --> 00:07:40,375
(Sighs)

167
00:08:03,941 --> 00:08:06,301
(Phone rings)

168
00:08:08,938 --> 00:08:09,949
Hello.

169
00:08:10,074 --> 00:08:11,150
Hey, it's Tyler.

170
00:08:11,275 --> 00:08:13,535
I've been trying
to get in touch with you.

171
00:08:15,161 --> 00:08:16,121
Siobhan?

172
00:08:16,287 --> 00:08:18,908
Are you there?

173
00:08:19,033 --> 00:08:19,749
Yeah, I'm here.

174
00:08:19,915 --> 00:08:22,627
I've been meaning to call you.

175
00:08:22,793 --> 00:08:24,921
I thought you'd be back
in Paris by now.

176
00:08:27,965 --> 00:08:29,259
(Gasps)

177
00:08:30,710 --> 00:08:32,846
(Gasps)
Oh, Mrs. Martin, you scared me!

178
00:08:33,013 --> 00:08:36,057
Claudine, I'm so sorry.

179
00:08:36,223 --> 00:08:37,476
Oh, no, it's okay.

180
00:08:37,601 --> 00:08:38,844
I just wasn't expecting you.

181
00:08:38,969 --> 00:08:40,228
It's so early.

182
00:08:40,394 --> 00:08:42,548
It's early for you, too.

183
00:08:42,673 --> 00:08:43,648
Olivia still cracking the whip?

184
00:08:43,814 --> 00:08:45,935
No, Ms. Charles is still in London.

185
00:08:46,060 --> 00:08:48,354
I just like to get a jump on the day.

186
00:08:48,479 --> 00:08:49,612
Can I help you with something?

187
00:08:49,778 --> 00:08:52,575
You know, maybe you can.

188
00:08:52,700 --> 00:08:53,867
Well, if you can keep a secret.

189
00:08:54,084 --> 00:08:55,368
(Grunts assent)

190
00:08:55,534 --> 00:08:57,746
