209
00:09:41,398 --> 00:09:42,874
You weren't sick yesterday.

210
00:09:43,040 --> 00:09:46,586
I started feeling badly when you
and Siobhan were at dinner.

211
00:09:46,752 --> 00:09:48,379
You ordered a pizza.
You're fine. Come on, Juliet.

212
00:09:48,545 --> 00:09:49,839
