253
00:11:22,431 --> 00:11:23,726
Would you keep the volume down?

254
00:11:23,851 --> 00:11:25,377
Look I get it... I understand

255
00:11:25,502 --> 00:11:26,894
that you're embarrassed or whatever,

256
00:11:27,060 --> 00:11:28,530
but it's not your fault.

257
00:11:28,655 --> 00:11:29,856
